      <h1>PHP &amp; Laravel,<br>from language fundamentals to framework internals</h1>
      <p>Ten core topics — PHP OOP, Composer/autoloading, the service container, providers &amp; facades, Eloquent, middleware/auth, queues &amp; events, the Repository/Service pattern you've actually shipped, caching &amp; the N+1 problem, and testing/Artisan — each broken down the same way as Chapter 1. Then 25 rapid-fire questions and a cheat sheet.</p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
